                    <history><provenance>The manuscript had very probably belonged to a church in the <placeName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LOC3577Gondar">Gondar</placeName> area, 
                        from where it was taken by
                        <persName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS9430Tewodros">Tewodros II</persName> and brought to <placeName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/INS0101MadhaneAlam">Madḫāne ʿĀlam</placeName>. It was then looted 
                        by the British <persName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS7484Napier">Napier</persName> expedition in <date>1868</date>.</provenance></history>
